00:25:07.250 --> 00:25:10.740
What you can do is using
the trades--

00:25:10.740 --> 00:25:14.358
the tricks of the trade of
modern historiography,

00:25:14.358 --> 00:25:17.854
you can play by the rules of
modern historiography and you

00:25:17.854 --> 00:25:20.000
