00:28:45.450 --> 00:28:50.461
Jesus of Nazareth in Latin,
rex King

00:28:50.461 --> 00:28:54.160
Iudaeorum of the Jews.
 

00:28:54.160 --> 00:28:55.970
Notice how though it's slightly
