00:28:55.970 --> 00:29:00.420
Let's look--if you've got your
Bibles it's Mark 15:26,

00:29:00.420 --> 00:29:03.858
if you've got a parallel
version, I'm going to be looking

00:29:03.858 --> 00:29:07.358
