00:29:12.640 --> 00:29:25.621
It's also Matthew 27:37,
it's also Luke 23:38,

00:29:25.621 --> 00:29:33.410
and it's also John 19:19.
 

00:29:33.410 --> 00:29:37.940
Now in Mark 15:26 it says,
